casebody.data:
George C. Jenks, as Administrator of the Estate of Amy V. Jenks, Deceased, Respondent, v. Veeder Contracting Company, Inc., et al., Appellants.

Reported below, 264 App. Div. 979.

Submitted January 4, 1943; decided January 7, 1943. John J. Conners, Jr., for motion.

No one opposed.

Motion dismissed, with ten dollars costs and necessary printing disbursements on the ground that an appeal lies as of right.
